        "timestamp": "2019-03-21 14:31:29.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review+1\n\nA couple notes about the status code: \na) how to maintain it in some way that is meaningful as you can get arbitrary exceptions, and would have to be maintained by underlying code?\nb) the second is overlap with http code, should offer more precision than the http status code, otherwise is just redundant.\nI don't have we have a good strategy across components to report status codes in a meaningful way.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
