        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n> A couple notes about the status code:\n > a) how to maintain it in some way that is meaningful as you can get\n > arbitrary exceptions, and would have to be maintained by underlying\n > code?\n > b) the second is overlap with http code, should offer more\n > precision than the http status code, otherwise is just redundant.\n > I don't have we have a good strategy across components to report\n > status codes in a meaningful way.\n\nYeah the redundancy I don't care for - but some projects just want to pull it from there for convenience.",
